snippet.title: Super Mario Universe - Reveal Trailer ! [Old Trailer]
snippet.description:
Super Mario Universe is a fan Mod of New Super Mario Bros U.
It aims for an new fun and unique adventure in a Universe you have never seen before.

      | What will it contain? |

- New Levels
- Custom Music
- Enemy Remodels 
- 6-7 World (We dont know yet)
- New Backgrounds
- New Tilesets
- Unique ideas 
- And so much more!
- And harv tilesets!!!

We are planning to release it 2022 but we are not really sure when it will be.
If you are interested in the mod you can join our discord server, we post there previews and other stuff about the mod.

  | Server Invite |

 https://discord.gg/f4fBHHZhGt

Trailer Theme by CubixL
